  "body": "develop e2c2d8e\n\nRun geth console.  use gasprice0\n\ncreate contract tx with following code and gas=500K\n\n```\n> cc = {from: '0x5288b347fec57748c522590149ea2e1b4cdaf787', to:'', value:0, gas:500000, gasPrice:0, data:jcode}\n{\n  data: '0x61007b8061000e600039610089566000607f537c01000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000006000350463c298557881141561007957610d0560006000a160166040604059905901600090526000815260028160200152809050205561115c6040604059905901600090526000815261115c816020015280905020555b505b6000f3',\n  from: '0x5288b347fec57748c522590149ea2e1b4cdaf787',\n  gas: 500000,\n  gasPrice: 0,\n  to: '',\n  value: 0\n}\n```\n\nsend and mine the tx, getBlock shows that gasUsed is 52554\n\n```\n{\n  difficulty: '132160',\n  extraData: '0x',\n  gasLimit: 3141592,\n  gasUsed: 52554,\n  hash: '0xf06c780a3a38ae6c873eb33211a430ad0eca669acd053e590aab2a51dc81b892',\n  logsBloom: '',\n  miner: '0x41fcb4160fdab4afbde9d7cad9effe8cc927e1fe',\n  nonce: '0x20b15ad68e599a2d',\n  number: 51,\n  parentHash: '0x6e65d089a61459d93cf249504ca4bf2cd366238fa0a9d88db33ac497103a1e88',\n  sha3Uncles: '0x1dcc4de8dec75d7aab85b567b6ccd41ad312451b948a7413f0a142fd40d49347',\n  size: 734,\n  stateRoot: '0xf5baaaf8f26378da779a47abc19ae5e7f6e932eb753198129efb44be202a5389',\n  timestamp: 1434054751,\n  totalDifficulty: '6871360',\n  transactions: [{\n    blockHash: '0xf06c780a3a38ae6c873eb33211a430ad0eca669acd053e590aab2a51dc81b892',\n    blockNumber: 51,\n    from: '0x5288b347fec57748c522590149ea2e1b4cdaf787',\n    gas: 500000,\n    gasPrice: '0',\n    hash: '0x0ee5d95911b4e2f2fa25a4cf2039ee30747b4f1addad038254437e5ac9b0fa2d',\n    input: '0x61007b8061000e600039610089566000607f537c01000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000006000350463c298557881141561007957610d0560006000a160166040604059905901600090526000815260028160200152809050205561115c6040604059905901600090526000815261115c816020015280905020555b505b6000f3',\n    nonce: 4,\n    to: Error: ,\n    transactionIndex: 0,\n    value: '0'\n  } ],\n  transactionsRoot: '0x3aebdc34590a903958618c331d7425b9234cf207503584f35cdc62d1e1d782a1',\n  uncles: [ ]\n}\n```\n\nSo let's create the same contract but this time using only 50K gas:\n\n```\n> cc\n{\n  data: '0x61007b8061000e600039610089566000607f537c01000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000006000350463c298557881141561007957610d0560006000a160166040604059905901600090526000815260028160200152809050205561115c6040604059905901600090526000815261115c816020015280905020555b505b6000f3',\n  from: '0x5288b347fec57748c522590149ea2e1b4cdaf787',\n  gas: '0xc350',\n  gasPrice: '0x0',\n  to: '',\n  value: '0x0'\n}\n```\n\nsend and mine the tx, getBlock shows that gasUsed is 27954:\n\n```\n{\n  difficulty: '132096',\n  extraData: '0x',\n  gasLimit: 3141592,\n  gasUsed: 27954,\n  hash: '0xb8eb6b6f1af62e8e829db7efd868af0b7fdc979142451869903cd4ecd02e061f',\n  logsBloom: '',\n  miner: '0x41fcb4160fdab4afbde9d7cad9effe8cc927e1fe',\n  nonce: '0x19f861e6bcb631f1',\n  number: 52,\n  parentHash: '0xf06c780a3a38ae6c873eb33211a430ad0eca669acd053e590aab2a51dc81b892',\n  sha3Uncles: '0x1dcc4de8dec75d7aab85b567b6ccd41ad312451b948a7413f0a142fd40d49347',\n  size: 733,\n  stateRoot: '0x50f98adf58183aaf85a3ae5281c9736ff7feb79ca364f3acf13e1649440c2c9a',\n  timestamp: 1434054930,\n  totalDifficulty: '7003456',\n  transactions: [{\n    blockHash: '0xb8eb6b6f1af62e8e829db7efd868af0b7fdc979142451869903cd4ecd02e061f',\n    blockNumber: 52,\n    from: '0x5288b347fec57748c522590149ea2e1b4cdaf787',\n    gas: 50000,\n    gasPrice: '0',\n    hash: '0xd9620092d61538463952f099e04150de10c641df24f258cff87b340c8be9443e',\n    input: '0x61007b8061000e600039610089566000607f537c01000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000006000350463c298557881141561007957610d0560006000a160166040604059905901600090526000815260028160200152809050205561115c6040604059905901600090526000815261115c816020015280905020555b505b6000f3',\n    nonce: 5,\n    to: Error: ,\n    transactionIndex: 0,\n    value: '0'\n  } ],\n  transactionsRoot: '0xc433de0cef967a6ad5ff6425337ce9baa61b349c986e7c27c35a7b61d988bba6',\n  uncles: [ ]\n}\n```\n\nThe 1st tx told us that creating the contract costs 52554 gas.  So when we only specify 50K gas, the expected result is that gasUsed will be 50K (it's all consumed due to outofgas).  But the 2nd tx says gasUsed is only 27954.\nEXPECTED: 50K gas used\nOBSERVED: 27954 gas used\n\nfromaccount balance is always 21K\n\n```\n> eth.getBalance('0x5288b347fec57748c522590149ea2e1b4cdaf787')\n'21000'\n```\n\nFWIW the contract code source is Serpent:\n\n```\ndata d[]\ndef foo():\n    log(3333)\n    self.d[2] = 22\n    self.d[4444] = 4444\n```\n\nWhen compiled with Serpent it gives:\n\n```\n61007b8061000e600039610089566000607f537c01000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000006000350463c298557881141561007957610d0560006000a160166040604059905901600090526000815260028160200152809050205561115c6040604059905901600090526000815261115c816020015280905020555b505b6000f3\n```\n\nNote: another minor issue is the output of getBlock has 'to: Error: '\n",
